<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <title>Amazon Seller Onboarding</title>
</head>
<body>

```
<h2>Amazon Seller Onboarding</h2>

<form action="onboarding" method="post">

    <label>Seller Name:</label><br>
    <input type="text" name="sellerName" placeholder="Enter name"><br><br>

    <label>Seller Mobile:</label><br>
    <input type="text" name="sellerMobile" placeholder="Enter mobile"><br><br>

    <label>Seller Email:</label><br>
    <input type="email" name="sellerEmail" placeholder="Enter email"><br><br>

    <label>Seller Type:</label><br>
    <input type="text" name="sellerType" placeholder="Individual / Company"><br><br>

    <input type="submit" value="Onboard Me!">

</form>
```

</body>
</html>
